function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idVampire) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idVampire,true)
		Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idVampire)
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	idVampire = idActorSpawned
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idVampire,false)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idVampire, ANIMKEY_TORTURED_BURNSTAND)
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idTorturer,true)
	Hydra.Wait(5)
	Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idVampire)
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)

	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idTorturer,true)
	Hydra.Wait(5)
	Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idVampire)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idVampire) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idVampire,true)
		Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idVampire)
	end
end
